# Data and State Management

## Data Files
The application uses static data files for content:

- [data/profile.ts](mdc:data/profile.ts) - Personal profile information
- [data/portfolio.ts](mdc:data/portfolio.ts) - Portfolio projects data
- [data/about.ts](mdc:data/about.ts) - About section data
- [data/blog.ts](mdc:data/blog.ts) - Blog posts data
- [data/social.ts](mdc:data/social.ts) - Social media links
- [data/menu.ts](mdc:data/menu.ts) - Navigation menu items
- [data/main.ts](mdc:data/main.ts) - Main configuration data

## State Management
The application uses Zustand for state management, with stores defined in the [store/](mdc:store/) directory.

Custom React hooks are available in the [hooks/](mdc:hooks/) directory.